                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                            oc:textContent "**Stateless vs stateful:** The snippet above creates a fresh transport per request (stateless). Fine for most API-wrapping servers. If tools need to share state across calls in a session (rare), use a session-keyed transport map — see the SDK's `examples/server/simpleStreamableHttp.ts`." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
